OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and patchy rain soon
OL,6,Fclearing this morning. Then bright
OL,7,Fspells with the odd shower in the
OL,8,Fwest, east mainly dry. Brisk
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds, becoming strong
OL,10,Fin the northwest this afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy in the northwest with
OL,13,Fsome showery rain overnight. Otherwise
OL,14,Fa dry night elsewhere with clear
OL,15,Fperiods. Strong southwesterly winds in
OL,16,Fthe northwest gradually easing down.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,19,Fwith a few showers in the west.
OL,20,FStaying largely dry across the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
