OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FPatchy
OL,6,Frain on Tuesday morning, a few heavy
OL,7,Fand slow moving showers breaking out
OL,8,Fin the afternoon. A few afternoon
OL,9,Fshowers on Wednesday. Rain followed by
OL,10,Fshowers on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
